ches/retro/enforcement.md, src/templates/verify-prompt.ts — all out of story scope)\n- **Coverage gaps:** None. All 158 files above 80% floor, 96.85% overall.\n- **Architecture concerns:** None.\n- **Items sent back for re-development:** None.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 22\n- By tool: Bash: 7, Read: 9, Edit: 4, Grep: 8, Glob: 1, Skill: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: `git diff --name-only` (~20 lines), `npx vitest run` (~15 lines), `npx codeharness coverage` (~5 lines)\n- Files read: 10 unique, 11 total reads\n- Redundant operations: One redundant story file read, two grep passes for black.box could have been combined\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":60,"oldLines":3,"newStart":60,"newLines":14,"lines":[" - Largest Bash outputs: `git diff --name-only` (~20 lines), `npx vitest run` (~15 lines), `npx codeharness coverage` (~5 lines)"," - Files read: 10 unique, 11 total reads"," - Redundant operations: One redundant story file read, two grep passes for black.box could have been combined","+","+### 16-7-update-knowledge-and-enforcement-docs — verification (2026-03-28T11:32)","+","+No issues reported. ALL_PASS (12/12 ACs).","+","+## Token Report","+- Total tool calls: 16","+- By tool: Bash: 7, Read: 2, Grep: 10","+- Largest Bash outputs: `npm test` (~50 lines), `npx vitest run` (~15 lines), `ls verification/` (~100 lines)","+- Files read: 2 unique, 2 total reads","+- Redundant operations: npm test run twice (once truncated, once via vitest for cleaner output)"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
